thread.title: BRIEF-Novabase Posts FY Net Profit Of 4.8 Mln Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Novabase Posts FY Net Profit Of 4.8 Mln Euros
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - NOVABASE SGPS SA:
* FY NET PROFIT 4.8 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 9.6 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA 10.9 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 5.9 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY TURNOVER 139.6 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 135.6 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* TO PROPOSE DIVIDEND OF 0.15 EUROS PER SHARE * SEES 2018 EBITDA OF 8 MILLION EUROS, 2018 TURNOVER OF 140 MILLION EUROS
Source text: bit.ly/2EW7mkC
